Package: mvp
Type: Package
Title: Fast Manipulation of Multivariate Polynomials
Version: 1.0-0
Date: 2018-12-01
Author: Robin K. S. Hankin
Depends: methods
Suggests: knitr,rmarkdown,spray
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Maintainer: Robin K. S. Hankin <hankin.robin@gmail.com>
Description: Fast manipulation of multivariate polynomials
  using the 'Map' class of the Standard Template Library.  The package
  uses print and coercion methods from the 'mpoly' package.  It is
  comparable in speed to the 'spray' package for sparse arrays, but
  retains the symbolic benefits of 'mpoly'.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.3),partitions,mpoly
LinkingTo: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: C++11
URL: https://github.com/RobinHankin/mvp.git
BugReports: https://github.com/RobinHankin/mvp/issues
